Vanessa Marquez (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vanessa_Marquez_(actress) 0 Vanessa Marquez (December 21, 1968 – August 30, 2018) was an American actress. She was primarily known for her recurring role on the first three seasons of ER as nurse Wendy Goldman, as well as her role as Ana Delgado in the 1988 teacher drama Stand and Deliver.
